items.title: Swiss deploy charm offensive in bid to slash crippling Trump tariffs
items.description: Swiss business leaders appear to have made progress with a private initiative in which reports say they brought gifts to the Oval Office.

items.title: Germany agrees new military service plan to boost troop numbers
items.description: The new military service plan will mandate all 18-year-old men to fill out a questionnaire on their suitability to serve.

items.title: US calls for international action to cut weapons supply to Sudan paramilitaries
items.description: "They're committing acts of sexual violence and atrocities," says the US secretary of state, "and it needs to end immediately".

items.title: Israel receives body Hamas says belongs to hostage
items.description: Confirmation of the remains would mean that only three deceased hostages' bodies now remain in Gaza.

items.title: Deadly Rio police raid failed to loosen gang's iron grip, residents say
items.description: More than 120 people were killed in the raid which targeted the Comando Vermelho criminal gang.
